{
  "info": {
    "name": "11. 🛡️ Moderation & Admin",
    "description": "Handles user reporting, content moderation, and admin dashboard controls. Standard users can create reports for tracks, albums, users, and comments. Admin roles are required for all `/admin/*` endpoints.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Create Report",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"entity_type\": \"Album\",\n  \"entity_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n  \"reason\": \"Copyright\",\n  \"description\": \"This album illegally reuses my artwork and audio without permission.\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/reports",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "reports"
          ]
        },
        "description": "## 1. Create Report\n\nAllows a registered user to flag a Track, Album, User, or Comment for moderation. Users cannot report their own entities.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (User)\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `entity_type` | String | Yes | Enum: `Track`, `Album`, `User`, `Comment`. |\n| `entity_id` | String | Yes | The MongoDB ObjectId of the entity being reported. |\n| `reason` | String | Yes | Enum: `Copyright`, `InappropriateContent`, `Spam`, `HateSpeech`, `Other`. |\n| `description` | String | No | Optional context provided by the user (Max 500 chars). |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "201 Created",
          "status": "Created",
          "code": 201,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"report\": {\n            \"_id\": \"65e2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2\",\n            \"reporter_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n            \"entity_type\": \"Album\",\n            \"entity_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n            \"reason\": \"Copyright\",\n            \"description\": \"This album illegally reuses my artwork and audio without permission.\",\n            \"status\": \"Pending\",\n            \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\n            \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\n            \"__v\": 0\n        }\n    }\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "400 Bad Request – Self Report",
          "status": "Bad Request",
          "code": 400,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"You cannot report your own account.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Get All Reports (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/reports?page=1&limit=20&status=Pending",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "reports"
          ],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "page",
              "value": "1",
              "description": "Pagination page number."
            },
            {
              "key": "limit",
              "value": "20",
              "description": "Items per page."
            },
            {
              "key": "status",
              "value": "Pending",
              "description": "Filter by status (Pending, Resolved, Dismissed)."
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "## 2. Get All Reports\n\nRetrieves a paginated list of all platform reports, including album reports. Used to populate the Admin Dashboard. The `reporter_id` is populated with the user's basic info.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (Admin Role Only)\n\n### Query Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n| `page` | Number | 1 | The current page. |\n| `limit` | Number | 20 | Results per page. |\n| `status` | String | None | Filter results by report status. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"reports\": [\n            {\n                \"_id\": \"65e2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2\",\n                \"reporter_id\": {\n                    \"_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n                    \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n                    \"email\": \"johndoe@example.com\"\n                },\n                \"entity_type\": \"Album\",\n                \"entity_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n                \"reason\": \"Copyright\",\n                \"description\": \"This album illegally reuses my artwork and audio without permission.\",\n                \"status\": \"Pending\",\n                \"admin_notes\": \"\",\n                \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\n                \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\n                \"__v\": 0\n            }\n        ],\n        \"total\": 1\n    }\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "403 Forbidden – Not Admin",
          "status": "Forbidden",
          "code": 403,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"error\": \"Forbidden: Admin access only.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Resolve Report (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"Dismissed\",\n  \"admin_notes\": \"Reviewed the album report. No action taken.\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/reports/:id/resolve",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "reports",
            ":id",
            "resolve"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "65e2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2",
              "description": "The Report ID"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "## 3. Resolve Report\n\nUpdates a report's status and logs the administrator's internal notes regarding their decision.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (Admin Role Only)\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `status` | String | Yes | Must be `Resolved` or `Dismissed`. |\n| `admin_notes` | String | Yes | Internal justification for the action taken. |\n\n### Moderation Scope\n\nThis endpoint matches the current track moderation flow: it only updates the report record and admin notes. It does not automatically hide or delete the underlying album or track."
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"report\": {\n            \"_id\": \"65e2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2\",\n            \"entity_type\": \"Album\",\n            \"entity_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n            \"reason\": \"Copyright\",\n            \"description\": \"This album illegally reuses my artwork and audio without permission.\",\n            \"status\": \"Dismissed\",\n            \"admin_notes\": \"Reviewed the album report. No action taken.\",\n            \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-13T11:00:00.000Z\"\n        }\n    }\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "404 Not Found",
          "status": "Not Found",
          "code": 404,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"fail\",\n    \"message\": \"Report not found.\"\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Suspend User (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "PUT",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/users/:id/suspend",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "users",
            ":id",
            "suspend"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1",
              "description": "The User ID to suspend"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "## 4. Suspend User\n\nImmediately flags a user account as suspended (`is_suspended: true`). The user will be blocked from logging in or utilizing platform services.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (Admin Role Only)"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"message\": \"User suspended\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"user\": {\n            \"_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n            \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n            \"is_suspended\": true\n        }\n    }\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Restore User (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "PUT",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/users/:id/restore",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "users",
            ":id",
            "restore"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1",
              "description": "The User ID to restore"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "## 5. Restore User\n\nRemoves the suspension flag from a user account (`is_suspended: false`), restoring full access to the platform.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (Admin Role Only)"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "200 OK",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "cookie": [],
          "body": "{\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"message\": \"User restored\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"user\": {\n            \"_id\": \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n            \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n            \"is_suspended\": false\n        }\n    }\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Block Track (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/tracks/:id/block",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "tracks",
            ":id",
            "block"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Blocks a track, making it unplayable across the platform."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "7. Unblock Track (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/tracks/:id/unblock",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "tracks",
            ":id",
            "unblock"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Restores a blocked track, making it playable again."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "8. Delete Track (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "DELETE",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/tracks/:id",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "tracks",
            ":id"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Permanently deletes a track and its S3 assets."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "9. Block Album (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/albums/:id/block",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "albums",
            ":id",
            "block"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Blocks an album (hides it), making it invisible across the platform."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "10. Unblock Album (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/albums/:id/unblock",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "admin",
            "albums",
            ":id",
            "unblock"
          ],
          "variable": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Restores a blocked album, making it visible again."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "11. Delete Album (Admin)",
      "request": {
